    "By exposing this risk, we aim to inspire the development of more advanced defense mechanisms and encourage AI companies to implement stricter security protocols in their model development and deployment processes.",
    "Ultimately, this research contributes to the ongoing effort to create safer and more reliable AI systems that can be trusted in various applications.",
